  <brief_title>Study of Human Monoclonal Antibody to Treat Mycosis Fungoides and Sezary Syndrome</brief_title>
  <official_title>Open Label, Dose Escalation, Followed by Open Label,Single Arm Clinical Trial of HuMax-CD4 in Patients With Mycosis Fungoides Type CTCL (Stage IB-IVB) or Sezary Syndrome Who Are Refractory or Intolerant to Targretin® (Bexarotene) and One Other Standard Therapy</official_title>
